nodes.text: Screen Idols: A Who's Who Guide to Star Wars: The Clone Wars

"Sceen Idols: A Who's Who Guide to Star Wars: The Clone Wars" or "The Clone Wars: A Who's Who Guide" was an article inside Star Wars Insider 103 that introduced the various characters in Star Wars: The Clone Wars film and TV series.

In Star Wars Insider 103, the article was given two different titles. On the contents page it was called "The Clone Wars: A Who's Who Guide", but at the start of the actual article, it was called "Sceen Idols: A Who's Who Guide to Star Wars: The Clone Wars".
